#Problem Statement:
	PackerApplication:
 		Application to combine all the files from the directory into one file.
	Input:	Directory containing files,  File which combines data of all file of the directory i.e packerFileName
	Output: Creates packerFileName combining the data of all files
		

	Unpacker Application:
		Application which reads the data from packer file and creates separate file as per data.
	Input:  PackerFile name
	Output: Creates file with data

	

	
